<h2 class="bold font-l">Misery | Hobbling scene</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Annie Wilkes holds novelist Paul Sheldon hostage and forces him to resurrect her favorite character in his book. She even resorts to breaking his ankles to keep him from leaving. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Yandere" class='trope-example-link'>Yandere</a></p>
</div>
</div>
